## 10. Fidelity Notes

shadows_detected: {true|false}
fonts_proprietary: ["{FONT_1}", "{FONT_2}"]
icons_not_captured: true
photography_not_captured: true
alpha_lost: []  # tokens where 8-digit hex was normalized to 6-digit per spec

## 11. Implementation

Stack: {STACK_FRAMEWORK} + Tailwind v{TAILWIND_VERSION} + shadcn/ui
Tailwind config: {TAILWIND_CONFIG}
Components root: {COMPONENT_SOURCE_ROOT}
Regenerate: {REGEN_CMD}

### Token → Tailwind utility mapping

| Token | Utility |
|---|---|
| `colors.primary` | `bg-primary text-primary-foreground` |
| `colors.background` | `bg-background text-foreground` |
| `rounded.button` | `rounded-md` (or custom) |
| `spacing.4` | `p-4 / m-4 / gap-4` |
